name: Impossible Dash Up - Touch to jump as far as you can & avoid the white tile
name_original: Impossible Dash Up - Touch to jump as far as you can & avoid the white tile
description:
How high can you dash?
Dash the ball as high as you can to beat your friends score! Be careful of those blocks and don't let it close on you. They are Dangerous!

It's difficult and addictive!! Once you start, you can't stop!
